## Unit 3: Lesson 08 - Creating Functions with Parameters

# Background

You can include more than one parameter in a single function. The order of the parameters is important. You can name parameters anything, but a good name will clearly indicate how the value is used in the program.

# Lesson

* Identify situations for creating functions with parameters.
* Incorporate functions with parameters into an “Under the Sea” digital scene. 


